drinking. He damaged his hotel room and was hospitalized for chest 
pains. 
</P>
<P>
	The former British and PGA Championship winner, Daly has  
finished no higher than 14th in seven events this season. 
</P>
<P>
	Last year, he had only two top-10 finishes. His most lasting  
image came at the Greater Vancouver Open, when he burst into tears 
and began shaking during the opening round. He said it was because 
of his battle with alcoholism. 
</P>
